!!! 5
html(lang="en")
  head
    title Factlink - Something went wrong
    link(rel="stylesheet", type="text/css", href= proxy_url + "/static/styles/error.css")
  body
    div#error
      h1 Factlink Browser

      div.bubble
        p The Factlink Browser enables Factlink on each page you visit.
        p
          | You can use the url bar above or do a
          a(href="javascript:parent.location.href='#{proxy_url}/?url=http://search.yahoo.com&factlinkModus=#{factlinkModus}'") web search
          |  to continue.